- replacement  
- re-implementation  

No permission is required.

---

## XII. CANON COMPATIBILITY

Any licensing or commercial structure referencing this document must remain
compatible with Canon.

Any structure introducing irreversible control, exit suppression, or authority
capture is invalid by definition.

---

## XIII. STATUS

- Canon: defined elsewhere, frozen  
- Layer 1: constraint interface  
- This document: operational reference  
- Future work: Layer 3 and beyond  

---

## FINAL NOTE

This document is correct if a reader can determine:

- how constraint violations are handled  
- how failure degrades power rather than concentrates it  
- how authority is prevented from emerging through operation  

without knowing who authored it, why it exists, or what system it runs on.

